<h1 class="nhsuk-heading-xl">A personalised digital care plan for sickle cell crisis care</h1>

<p class="nhsuk-lead-paragraph">
  People with sickle cell disease do not reliably receive timely pain relief during an acute
  painful crisis, and too often experience poor care. This project delivers a personalised,
  portable digital care plan — to make crisis care faster, more accessible, more trustworthy,
  and more accountable.
</p>

<div class="nhsuk-care-card nhsuk-care-card--non-urgent">
  <div class="nhsuk-care-card__heading-container">
    <h2 class="nhsuk-care-card__heading"><span role="text">A programme of the {{ site.owner }}</span></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="nhsuk-care-card__content">
    <p>Informed by the Observatory’s 2022–23 research with University Hospitals Bristol and Weston,
    this programme commissions the build of a new digital service, developed in the open.</p>
  </div>
</div>

