<div class="callout-stat">
  <p class="nhsuk-body-l">“No one’s listening.” Repeated reports and inquests have found that people with
  sickle cell — predominantly from Black communities — face delays, dismissal and substandard
  care during crises. A well-designed care plan is one practical, evidence-informed response.</p>
</div>

